review_blob: The beer is readily available at most Wegmans that Ive been to so I finally bought it.  Its citrusy, carbonated, and forgetfull.  Meaning its an IPA, nothing more, nothing less.

Bought this beer at Beers of the World in Rochester.  Well worth the 6-7 bucks/22 oz bottle.  A must, in my opinion if you like IPAs.  As soon as I popped the cap my mouth was at the top and I was able to inhale a great flavor.  It got even better as I actually drank the beer.  I rated the appearance a 3 out of 5 since I didnt even pour it out of the bottle.
Bought this beer at Beers of the World in Rochester.  Well worth the 11 bucks/4 pack.  A must in my opinion if you like IPAs.

Bought this at Beers of the World, 3450 Winton Place, Rochester, NY.  Not sure whats more aggressive, the beer or the hype printed on the label.  Ill spend my 6 bucks/22 oz elsewhere next time.
